don't even feel]92 [they are financially well off.]93

[Many of the affluent aren't comfortable with themselves, either.]94
[About 40% don't feel]95 [they're more able than others.]96 [While
twothirds feel some guilt]97 [about being affluent,]98 [only 25% give
